{
  "stem": "4226.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was-- I don't know whether that food was for them or for us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because if, if what, what we found out that the transport should, should have ended in, in southern Bavaria, in, in southern Tyrol, a place called-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] not [INAUDIBLE]-- Mittenwald.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "M-I-T-T-E-N-W-A-L-D, Mittenwald.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in Mittenwald, they had a ravine which was prepared to massacre prisoners by machine guns.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Setup with different angles and everything else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They only needed a handful of, of submachine guns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You could-- they could kill thousands in, in a matter of hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But that's how it happens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we, we, we got next day, about 11 o'clock, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Americans arrived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "B The first one-- we saw tanks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We thought they are Russians, because they had the five stars, white stars with broken circle silk screened onto them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we never knew the Americans have a five star like the Russians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russian stuff is red, they have it white.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they came closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then everybody come out of the wagons and go in front of them in the roadway.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- some spoke Yiddish, some officers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And some could speak a bit-- whatever language they could speak, they spoke to, to the people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we saw the Russian women there, talking to the guards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're pulling their hair out, handfuls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "SS guards, the women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The women guards.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when these Americans were the first tank unit, they-- each time the, the Germans put up some submachine in the bush, they were stopping and hitting that bush until 10, 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no, no leaves left on, on, on the trees there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they kept going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't, didn't take much risk, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we left the camp from Allach--",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
